Large square shaft. 290 x 2.90m depth 9m. top wall bricked. Stele in rubbish above shaft. Also few bl. gl. beads, fragments & a broken ushabtia. Frags of bl. gl. bowl & lid. Small cylindrical beads. Pair of horns. goat or ram. Fragt. of v. late pottery. Half a limestone figure, rough wala. female with ibig. The grave is clearly late & later still the shaft was filled up with fragments of mummies. OVER.
info.comments: Some of the handwriting was difficult to decipher. I made my best possible judgement.
